When I upgrade it is very difficult to know what plug-ins will work on the new version.  It would be great to have a button beside each plug-in which is installed on the system with a Test button.  When I upgrade on my QA server I can go through the repository and click Test Plugin button and it would test the macros for that plug-in and let me know if it works or fails.  Even if this is only done for supported plug-ins it will make us all aware of what plug-ins will continue to work on the new version and which ones will not.

